RMBI</a></span>) is a small regional bank that hasn\u2019t any specific competitive advantage in the banking sector, thus one of its most attractive features of its investment case was its above-average dividend</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977075709/image_1977075709.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742781-richmond-mutual-bancorporation-risk-return-profile-not-attractive-for-long-term-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:05:06"}, {"id": "4742787", "title": "U.S. IPO Weekly Recap: ServiceTitan Launches As Small Issuers Slip Through The IPO Window", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"IPO Initial Public Offering 3d concept\" data-id=\"1299608214\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"4500px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Olemedia</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Four small IPOs priced this past week, joined by two SPACs.</p> <p>The biggest news came from software provider <strong>ServiceTitan</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TTAN\" title=\"ServiceTitan, Inc.\">TTAN</a>), which kicked off the roadshow for its $480 million offering. It's expected to price in the week ahead.</p> <p>Neuro-inflammation</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1299608214/image_1299608214.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742787-us-ipo-servicetitan-launches-small-issuers-slip-through-ipo-window", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4742779", "title": "Enterprise Products Partners: Unusual Insider Activities Signal Strong Buy Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Buy Text And Red Arrows On White Background\" data-id=\"1145882559\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1145882559/image_1145882559.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/