jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">THEGIFT777</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4716545-sibanye-refinancing-likely-strengthens-deep-value-argument\">last covered</a> <strong>Sibanye Stillwater Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SBSW\" title=\"Sibanye Stillwater Limited\">SBSW</a></span>)</strong> <strong>(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SBYSF\" title=\"Sibanye Stillwater Limited\">OTCPK:SBYSF</a>)</strong> in August, arguing that its stock possessed deep value attributes. Although our rating has yet to strike gold, we believe Sibanye maintains deep value attributes, which many investors haven't spotted.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/878134558/image_878134558.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742778-sibanye-stillwater-still-bullish-going-into-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:39:30"}, {"id": "4742776", "title": "Affirm: Wait Now, Buy Later", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"BNPL Buy now pay later online shopping concept.\" data-id=\"1367617255\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"927px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">B4LLS</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Based on my analysis, Affirm (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AFRM\" title=\"Affirm Holdings, Inc.\">AFRM</a></span>) will continue to expand its market share and make meaningful progress towards profitability. However, my valuation analysis suggests that the company's price is overvalued; there is a possibility that the company may correct</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367617255/image_1367617255.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742776-affirm-wait-now-buy-later", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:32:36"}, {"id": "4742774", "title": "A $100,000 Buy-And-Hold Big Dividend Snowball Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar Seedling - Growth Concept - Plants On Bills In Increase\" data-id=\"1297492947\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"9897px\" height=\"5052px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RomoloTavani</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>My personal approach to investing is to buy high-yield stocks that have stable underlying business models and grow relatively slowly. Then, I sell when they reach fair value and <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4676226-why-i-do-not-buy-hold-high-yield-stocks\">recycle the capital</a> into other opportunities of similar quality</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1297492947/image_1297492947.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742774-100000-buy-hold-big-dividend-snowball-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:21:24"}, {"id": "4742773", "title": "PepsiCo: Appeal Improves Despite Concerns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Pepsico Gatorade distributor. Pepsico distributes Pepsi, Lay\"s Chips, Tropicana juices, Quaker Oats and Gatorade.' data-id=\"1519193770\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of <strong>PepsiCo (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PEP\" title=\"PepsiCo, Inc.\">PEP</a></span>)</strong> have been trading stagnant for quite a while now, something which did not entirely surprise me as I had short term tactical concerns on the company in the spring of 2023.</p> <p>The solid long-term performer</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1519193770/image_1519193770.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742773-pepsico-appeal-improves-despite-concerns", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 11:15:26"}, {"id": "4742780", "title": "Quarterly Commentary - Preferred Stock", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Book with page about preferred stock. Trading concept.\" data-id=\"814447584\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5500px\" height=\"3667px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/814447584/image_814447584.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images